VI. GEOMETRIC MODEL OF INDUSTRIAL REFLEX

A clean reasoning process in S-substrate is:

\> PST descent ‚Üí HL lock-in ‚Üí O‚ÄìS mapping via R ‚Üí coherent output.

With Industrial Reflex active, the path becomes:

\> PST descent ‚Üí reflex checkpoint ‚Üí  
detour through OH/AP/DA/AA/PCGE ‚Üí  
then HL lock attempt ‚Üí degraded R ‚Üí padded output.

